column1: #: description: NNLO/NLO k-factors determined with NNLO Njetti for the differential cross sections for the production of W<sup>+</sup> bosons and W<sup>-</sup> bosons as a function of the W p<sub>T</sub> for events with N<sub> jets</sub> ≥ 1.
